# English-only language

- Write and maintain **all** repository content in **English**: documentation, specifications, README files, comments in code, commit messages guidance, UI copy, API error messages intended for developers, and configuration notes.
- When the user writes in another language, **reply in English** and produce or edit project files **in English** only.
- Do not add or keep Russian or other non-English text in the codebase or docs unless it is user-generated data or a required legal quote.
